  m_text: "The Door System for the facility is electronic, the lights indicating
    its state.\n\nGreen: Opened\nRed: Locked\n\nThe System sometimes fails, when
    this occurs please repair Immediately. \n\nSystem terminals and compound resources
    should be used..."
